I think of singing = Psalm of Veeshan and Niv's Harmonic.  Are there any other crucial songs out there that are singing based?
<br />

<br />
In many cases when not raiding I do not think of singing as being crucial (situational).  If you're raiding, your pov will be useless without some type of singing mod though<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /> 1.5 is pretty weak though knowing that epic is 1.8 and the vp quest is 2.0 and epic 1.5 is 2.2 (though tough quest).
