				<td colspan="2"><span>Concentrate on epic, it is a necessary evil until you can find greater mods later on.  Aside from brass you have no other worn mods, I still remember the pita of instrument switching and refuse to do it anymore unless absolutely neccessary.  1.5 is a weak singing mod but after a ton of aa, amp and harmonize there is little noticeable difference once you hit caps.  Singing is pbly the most important mod specifically because of Psalm of Veeshan though, when you meet a mobs that have chromatic resist (resist checks are done on a sum of all resists instead of just one) ae's you will be thankful for high singing mods.  Hi2u M'shas.
<br />

<br />
Use that saved money to buy armor upgrades, there were a number of attuneable plate drops that are running pretty cheap (at least on solro).  Replace your low hp slots first.  Arms head ear shoulders.  Haste is a luxury as bard melee dps is laughable till high dmg low delay ep/time weapons and tons of melee aa.  HP &gt; AC &gt; Resists &gt; Effect &gt; Stats in my opinion.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
